    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761310/extras/e18335d903287aa8628d3084c012f028.poster.avif?t=1767963727\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761310/extras/e18335d903287aa8628d3084c012f028.webm?t=1767963727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761310/extras/e18335d903287aa8628d3084c012f028.mp4?t=1767963727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paragrowth is Survival RPG game, placed in giant and dark forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge and explore areas mysteriously overgrown by trees and living roots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover history about the place and find useful equipment to help you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel further and meet few of other survivors, which can help you understand what's going on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your target might not be just survive, but something more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761310/extras/5ae78667c58573a0387aaa5993e7b8a9.poster.avif?t=1767963727\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761310/extras/5ae78667c58573a0387aaa5993e7b8a9.webm?t=1767963727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761310/extras/5ae78667c58573a0387aaa5993e7b8a9.mp4?t=1767963727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find hideout to survive nights full of paranormal activities and to hide from deadly monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare building and survive until soon rise up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt mutating prey for ingredients to make yourself mutate with forest but in controllable way and inject enemies abilities into yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Check link to our discord server on the right side of this page</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Flow:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When area you're in is completely explored, you can prepare for big travel through underground tunnels to enter new unique area (no way back) of the same map size, find new shelter, beware of murderous creatures and find new resources to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761310/extras/8448942c91b5be2ec7b9a76c9a4b1902.poster.avif?t=1767963727\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761310/extras/8448942c91b5be2ec7b9a76c9a4b1902.webm?t=1767963727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761310/extras/8448942c91b5be2ec7b9a76c9a4b1902.mp4?t=1767963727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maps will be generated procedurally, as well as most of the buildings and small areas placed on map, to make each area exploration unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free to switch for interaction FPS camera to handle indoor physical elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game is full of custom procedural animations giving more organic feel for characters and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game also features the custom expansive sound system for precise audio modulation inside buildings as well as audio waves behavior in the forest (far animals/creatures sounds)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Is Currently In Early Stage Of Development.</h2>",
